# Mission System UI/UX Plan

## Core UI Elements
- Mission Tracker Panel: List active missions, objectives, status
- Mission Details View: Show description, objectives, rewards
- Notifications: Mission start, complete, fail
- Integration with minimap/TimeMap (optional)

## UX Goals
- Clear feedback for mission progress
- Easy to track multiple missions
- Minimal UI clutter

## Implementation Notes
- Start with a simple sidebar or overlay
- Use existing UI component patterns
- Expand to support filtering, sorting, and notifications

